Field Standards
	entity		The monitored endpoint (hostname, container name, AWS instance, etc)
	metric_type	The type of monitor (cpu, filesystem) - top level grouping
	metric_value	The value of that metric
	metric_instance	An instance of a monitored entity (Total, /opt)
	metric_name	The name of a specific metric to be collected (cpu_idle, fs_used)	
	alert_operator	An operator used in evaluating thresholds
	alert_threshold	The threshold against which to measure a metric
	support_team	The support queue to send the alert to
	alert_tag	A list of tags applied to an alert which can be used to identify or group it

Metrics	
	Get last metric
		/api/v1/metric/last?entity=<host>&metric_type=<x>&metric_instance=<x>&metric_value=<x>&metric_name=<x>
	Get metric range
		/api/v1/metric/range?entity=<host>&metric_type=<x>&metric_instance=<x>&metric_value=<x>&metric_name=<x>&time_start=<x>&time_end=<x>

Entity Centric
  GET /api/v1/entity DONE
	Desc : Get list/single entity/entities that has/have been registered with portal
	Mandatory : None
	Optional : entity=<x>
	Default : entity=*
	Returns : JSON object/list with entity_name/platform/last_registered

Config Centric
  GET /api/v1/config/entity DONE
	Desc : Get configuation for an endpoint
	Mandatory : entity=<x>
	Optional : mode=live|custom
	Default : mode=live
	Returns : Array of configs for full / JSON structure for individual

  GET /api/v1/config/fragment DONE
	Desc : Return details of a config fragment
	Mandatory : None
	Optional : name=<x>
	Default : name=*
	Returns : Text document for config fragment

  GET /api/v1/config/alert DONE
	Desc : Get Alert definition 
	Mandatory : None
	Optional : entity=<x>
	Default : entity=*
	Returns : Array of documents for all hosts / JSON structure for individual host

Metric Centric
  GET /api/v1/metric/last 
	Desc : Get last value for a given metric
  GET /api/v1/metric/range 
	Desc : Get metric values over a timeframe

  POST /api/v1/metric
	Desc : Post a new metric DONE
	Mandatory : entity=<x>&app_id=<x>&metric_name=<x>&metric_value=<x>
	Options : None
	Default : None
	Returns : URL to view metric in portal

Alert Centric
  GET /api/v1/alert/history
	Desc : View alert history for given entity
  GET /api/v1/alert/last
	Desc : View most recent result for a given alert config

